    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors against the MRL 5 requirements for the VAD COU. Seven factors were assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. Despite these gaps, the submission is accepted at this stage under the Minimal profile for record-keeping purposes, pending completion of the full-profile assessment with structured requirement traceability. All project requirements were reviewed in narrative form; structured bindsRequirement linkage will be established in the subsequent full-profile package.",
